title: 175 High-Impact Cover Letter.pdf
description:
175 High-Impact Cover Letters THIRD EDITION
Author: Richard H. Beatty



To the legions of job seekers who, during my years as an employment executive, sent me thousands-upon-thousands of cover letters and resumes.

I have seen them all, both the good and the bad! You helped me appreciate what a truly good cover letter can do for the job seeker.
Thank you!
